speech: I think Batman is a necessary evil, vigilantism is the only solution given the level of corruption in Gotham
Vigilantes like Batman are what make Gotham great - the police haven't done anything about super villains, who would? Who could!?
Good guy - cool sense of style.
Batman is great, cleaning up the streets one criminal at a time. Guy should get a key to the city if you ask me.
Vigilante, hero, whatever you want to call him he's killing it. Figuratively, of course.
